title: Rubio raises about $6 million in third quarter, has $11 million on hand
text: LAS VEGAS -- Sen. Marco Rubio raised about $6 million for his presidential campaign in the third quarter of this year and entered the month of October with about $11 million on hand, campaign officials told top donors here Thursday.
